Intranet Translator | Linguistic technologies | Translation white paper | Intranet dictionaries | Specialized dictionaries | Download translator | Download dictionary | Translation Memory | Translation Management System | Translate your website | Théo Hoffenberg

                                               This online translator provides translations for words, short texts, phrases and idioms in French, Spanish, Italian, German, Russian, Portuguese, Hebrew and Japanese. Translation tools include: translation memory such as Across, Trados, SDL, Dejà Vu, as well as instant translation systems and machine translation like Reverso, BabelFish, Systran. Online dictionaries are from Collins, Merriam-Webster, Larousse, LEO, Oxford and Langenscheidt.
                                                


